ASABA – As the National Sports Festival commences on Thursday, Delta State Governor, Senator Ifeanyi Okowa has promised Team Delta the sum of N1 million for every gold medal won. The Governor made the promise yesterday at the Stephen Keshi Stadium, while addressing the state contingent shortly before their departure for Abuja, host to the festival. “You have worked very hard in the last three weeks, it is time to harvest the medals; you are Team Delta, remember that there is no team that will be like Team Delta and I believe your coaches have been doing very well,” he said. “For every gold, you will get N1 million, so, if you are not prepared for gold, work harder to get gold; for every Silver medal N500,000 while every Bronze medallist will get N250, 000. Be prayerful and confident.”